Median
========================================================
- Robust to Outliers
- For Ordered Data, Given by the Middle Term
- Must Average Two Terms Where n of Terms is Even
- The Smallest Value of i that Satisfies the Inequality

$$\sum_{i=1}^{j} f_i ≥ \frac{n+1}{2}$$

